 \u2018Anyone who divorces his wife must give her a written divorce paper.\u2019 ","But I tell you that anyone who divorces his wife forces her to be guilty of adultery. The only reason for a man to divorce his wife is if she has sexual relations with another man. And anyone who marries that divorced woman is guilty of adultery.","\u201cYou have heard that it was said to our people long ago
