 but your Father
 whom you cannot see
 will see you. Your Father sees what is done in secret
 and he will reward you.","\u201cDon\u2019t store treasures for yourselves here on earth where moths and rust will destroy them and thieves can break in and steal them.","But store your treasures in heaven where they cannot be destroyed by moths or rust and where thieves cannot break in and steal them.","Your heart will be where your treasure is.","\u201cThe eye is a light for the body. If your eyes are good
