 and all of you are brothers. ","Do not call any man here on earth your father. There is only one Father and He is in heaven.","You are not to be called leader. There is only one Leader and He is Christ.","\u201cHe who is greatest among you will be the one to care for you.","The person who thinks he is important will find out how little he is worth. The person who is not trying to honor himself will be made important.","\u201cIt is bad for you
