\u2019 do not go to see. Or if they say
 \u2018See! He is in the inside room
\u2019 do not believe them. ","The Son of Man will come as fast as lightning shines across the sky from east to west.","Birds gather wherever there is a dead body.","\u201cAs soon as those days of trouble and pain and sorrow are over
