\u2019 when you have a beam in your own eye? ","You hypocrite! First remove the beam from your own eye. Then you will see clearly to remove the piece of sawdust from another believer\u2019s eye.","\u201cDon\u2019t give what is holy to dogs or throw your pearls to pigs. Otherwise
 they will trample them and then tear you to pieces.","\u201cAsk
