 your whole body will be full of darkness. If then the light in you is darkness
 how great is the darkness!","\u201cNo one can serve two masters; for a slave will either hate the one and love the other
 or be devoted to the one and despise the other. You cannot serve God and wealth.","\u201cTherefore I tell you
