 \u2018Lord
 when did we see you hungry; or thirsty
 or a stranger
 or naked
 or sick
 or in prison
 and did not minister to You?\u2019","\u201cThen He shall answer them
 and say
 \u2018Truly I say to you
 inasmuch as you did not do it to one of the least of these
