 and the righteous into life eternal.\u201d","\u201cYou know that after two days is the Passover
 and the Son of Man shall be delivered to be crucified.\u201d","And Jesus
 knowing it
 said to them
 \u201cWhy do you trouble the woman? For she has done a good work for Me.","\u201cFor you have the poor with you always. But Me you shall not have always.","\u201cFor in pouring this ointment on My body
 she did it for My burial.","\u201cTruly I say to you
