 \u201cTruly I say to you that one of you shall betray Me.\u201d","And He answered and said
 \u201cThe one who dipped his hand in the dish with Me
 he shall betray Me.","\u201cSurely the Son of Man goes his way
 as it is written of Him. But woe to that man by whom the Son of Man is betrayed. It had been good for that man if he had never been born.\u201d","\u201cThen Judas (who betrayed Him) answered
 and said
 \u201cIs it me
 Master?\u201d He said to him
