 He gave it to them
 saying
 \u201cDrink all of it.","\u201cFor this is My blood of the New Testament
 which is shed for many
 for the remission of sins.","\u201cI say to you that I will not drink from the fruit of the vine again until that Day when I shall drink it new with you in my Father\u2019s Kingdom.\u201d","Then said Jesus to them
 \u201cAll of you will fall away from Me this night. For it is written
 \u2018I will strike the Shepherd
 and the sheep of the flock shall be scattered.\u2019","\u201cBut after I am risen again
 I will go before you into Galilee.\u201d","Jesus said to him
 \u201cTruly I say to you that this night
