 the one who betrays Me is here.\u201d","Then Jesus said to him
 \u201cFriend
 why have you come?\u201d Then they came and laid hands on Jesus and took Him.","Then Jesus said to him
 \u201cPut your sword back in its place. For all that take up the sword
