 and He will give Me more than twelve legions of angels?","\u201cHow then would the Scriptures be fulfilled which say that it must be so?\u201d","At that time
 Jesus said to the multitude
 \u201cYou have come out as against a thief
 with swords and clubs to take Me. Every day I sat among you
 teaching in the Temple
 and you did not take Me.","\u201cBut all this has been done so that the Scriptures of the Prophets might be fulfilled.\u201d Then all the disciples abandoned Him and fled.","Jesus said to him
 \u201cYou have said it. Nevertheless
 I say to you
 hereafter you shall see the Son of Man
 sitting at the right hand of Power
 and coming in the clouds of the heaven.","Then Peter remembered the words of Jesus
